data.title: Jake — The Regal Fund
data.text:
As a seasoned real estate professional, Jake Dean brings decades of experience and expertise to the table. He prides himself in a life filled with intentional redirection as he actively pursues excellence in every aspect of his life. His clients see and recognize this passion. Jake continuously recognizes and values the trust of his clients and daily strives to exceed their expectations.

Jake is known for his reputation for building high-quality relationships with investors, prominent business professionals, and distinguished community leaders. He truly enjoys creating and establishing high-level sales teams, top-notch client relations, and secure wealth management.

Jake’s real estate career boasts a plentitude of multifaceted transactions that include commercial, residential, turnkey rental properties, and major real estate investments. Over the last few years, he has built a multi-family syndication network spanning from the Southeast to the Southwest areas of the country. With deals in FL, GA, TN, TX, and the greater Chicago area, Jake controls units with a total value of over $54MM.

He is also a leader at The Multifamily Mindset, an education company that provides new and seasoned investors with the training and support they need to acquire multi-family properties. Jake has been a fundamental part in training hundreds of investors to acquire multi-family properties, establish and maintain a positive mindset, and reach their highest goals.

Jake has a true passion for teaching, inspiring, and lifting others. He is well known for his ability to command any room, from classroom to convention hall, with his positive tone as he shares the knowledge he has gained as a lifelong learner. With his philosophy that life itself is a learning process, he regularly attends and participates in investor related seminars and masterminds to constantly improve strategy and learn new skills.

As an avid golfer, Jake enjoys spending his spare time on the course with friends and colleagues. With a previous history in MMA fighting, he also spends time continuing to train in the martial arts. Continual practice and betterment of his abilities has always been pivotal in his personal and professional life. This is what makes Jake unique and a fundamental asset to hundreds of clients and investors as they rely on his expertise: his innate ability to achieve work/life balance with joy and intention.
